commitMessage:
Bug 578124 - [Code Clean-Up] "Reduce indentation" is missing expression

Example:

if (!(args != null)) {
    System.out.println("null args: we should not be here");
} else {
    return;
}

Result:

if (MISSING) {
    return;
}
System.out.println("null args: we should not be here");

